com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.commands.sdr.record

Class FruDeviceLocatorRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.commands.sdr.record.SensorRecord
      • com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.commands.sdr.record.FruDeviceLocatorRecord

  • public class FruDeviceLocatorRecord
extends SensorRecord
    This record is used for locating FRU information that is on the IPMB, on a Private Bus behind or management controller, or accessed via FRU commands to a management controller.
